  "f_stage_differences": {
    "cmapss_to_ncmapss_changes": "1. data_loader.py: HDF5 reader with whitelist (replaces flat-text reader). 2. data_loader.py: cruise-phase filter (TRA stability + altitude). 3. data_loader.py: per-cycle mean aggregation (within-flight -> cycle-level). 4. data_loader.py: regime normalization on flight conditions W (replaces operating-settings normalization). 5. config.py: 14 named sensors mapped to HDF5 column order (replaces 21 numbered sensors). Reused unchanged: feature_extraction.py, failure_basin.py, evaluation.py, manifold_projection.py. The W stage (USE_CAUSAL_WEIGHTS=False) and M stage (LDA 1-component) are identical to original C-MAPSS.",
